title: BRIEF-Equimaxx decreases stake in Power Price to 17.98 pct

BRIEF-Equimaxx decreases stake in Power Price to 17.98 pct Sept 3 
Sept 3 Power Price SA : 
* Equimaxx Llc decreases stake in company to 17.98 percent from 21.11 percent via sale of 813,617 shares on Aug. 12 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
